/*
Clean up detik.com website (remove ads), change background to clean white. Tidy up page layout. 

NB: Hello..Pak Nicko... kalo mo baca detik.com tanpa iklan, pake tool beginian nih...

What is Detik.com?
***Detik.com is one of leading Indonesian online news provider, but I am sick of its advertisement, they keep adding ads till the whole page is cluttered. 
Without this style sheet, browsing detik.com is like browsing "Ads portal" with featured news.
With this style sheet, it become News portal with no ads! 

We are continuously improving this style-sheet.
This covers not only main page, but also detik finance, detik sport, detik inet and other affiliated websites.

jiraiya2005@gmail.com
*/

